to the editor re doctor spurns euphemism in pursuing abortion rights public lives column april 7 your profile of dr leroy carhart provides inspiration to those of us who are disheartened by the almost daily attempts to erode our civil rights dr carhart is an american hero he continues to work within the framework of the legal system to provide women with a choice that is still guaranteed by the constitution despite the efforts of extralegal extremists who have used violence to try to intimidate dr carhart into giving up his right to offer abortions to women who need them he has remained committed to his cause your column was a profile in courage if ever there was one lorraine c gray seattle april 8 2000

